# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies
**/node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# testing
**/coverage/
**/blob-report/
**/playwright-report/
**/test-results/

# build and tool output
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/out/

# misc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# environment files
.env*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example

# vercel
**/.vercel/

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# local Serena working memory; reviewed shared memories remain tracked
.serena/memories/local/

# package-manager cache created by sandboxed validation
.pnpm-store/

.vercel
.env*
